    <item>
      <title>お名前.comで取得したドメインを使用してACMでSSL証明書を発行する</title>
      <link>/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;表題の通り、お名前.comで取得したドメインを使用してACMでSSL証明書を発行する際のメモ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;acmからパブリック証明書をリクエスト&#34;&gt;ACMからパブリック証明書をリクエスト&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134641278&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_aaca63ea9856066bdb82ec8386f02bf8.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_5ac7e6909ea598d9481ee84e5ea5c58a.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_aaca63ea9856066bdb82ec8386f02bf8.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;296&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ドメイン名と検証方法を入力&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134754419&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_89c3744f356356ac48a9480d70426906.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_0c8ce4bfb00a24b535bcd4cca0fdc584.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_89c3744f356356ac48a9480d70426906.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;596&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;証明書の発行中。しばらく待機する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134832140&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_8ad648f1fea79243ec0d27891b18c469.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_689e97f82bc3e00f06c0d0b8cc82e3bb.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_8ad648f1fea79243ec0d27891b18c469.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;123&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;証明書の詳細画面に移動して、「CSVにエクスポート」を選択して手元にダウンロードしておく。後続の手順で参照。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135511287&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_90e5c3c86fc87146897851a0270a78e0.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_724fce8c23d692142ef614ab3c3ae7ef.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_90e5c3c86fc87146897851a0270a78e0.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;303&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;お名前.comに移動して「DNSレコードを設定する」に移動&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135631643&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_ca0b39cae44a689f67f8a03b23e872ed.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_6e0b40329400f7a6802662c8312fd9e6.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_ca0b39cae44a689f67f8a03b23e872ed.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;390&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;対象ドメインを選択して次へ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135711384&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_7277a8416af8f8d1b6874779e38b2182.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_2047e6beb8f2320e01f5093c3cad9979.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_7277a8416af8f8d1b6874779e38b2182.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;457&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DNSレコード設定を利用する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135824174&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_dc6cbb9a908724c7bfede03a90c68c35.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_b5329949de974f9a98786dbe34a03664.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_dc6cbb9a908724c7bfede03a90c68c35.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;665&#34;
               height=&#34;760&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ACMの画面から下記のようなCSVをダウンロードしているはずなのでここから下記を入力する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140655648&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_1b69e7d75bb41bc305f42d9ec7e859bf.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_ec9ec2f91bb9fcfc60df4e035a704f7b.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_1b69e7d75bb41bc305f42d9ec7e859bf.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;163&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;ホスト名&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;TYPE&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;VALUE&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Domain Name&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;CNAME&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Record Value&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;入力して追加する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140548910&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_9737bf25085fb4d706d01f248da1bfa2.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_b57cbbc9f64500ba9de8732c88f1e133.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_9737bf25085fb4d706d01f248da1bfa2.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;215&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ページ下部の設定はデフォルトのままチェックを付ける&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140711412&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_1311d7e1a5b3f8b0ab55bf9bb2be5a9a.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_6f3303ce00fd89af90e3bf0cd9858a9f.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_1311d7e1a5b3f8b0ab55bf9bb2be5a9a.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;257&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;設定するをクリック&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140751547&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_44067ec654d84c2d08faad05a028c6d6.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_300304abca726446e9fcbe5e2c92a503.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_44067ec654d84c2d08faad05a028c6d6.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;687&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;完了となる&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140823966&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_839c4e790e19e8438f6c0dd3d5ddf5df.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_79d00ec27eabdbe9b4fcbe138ff093ae.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_839c4e790e19e8438f6c0dd3d5ddf5df.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;121&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;数時間から24時間程度と書かれているのでDNSの伝搬に時間が掛かるので気長に待つ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://help.onamae.com/answer/8081&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://help.onamae.com/answer/8081&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112141220725&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_91d5c7bbf6a84e60167b088aee1e93d4.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_24805469eb12fa4bdd0ae3a285329eef.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_91d5c7bbf6a84e60167b088aee1e93d4.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;436&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;数十分でステータスが発行済に変更になった&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112142634611&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_78d037005654202b635b5ad986d36486.webp 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_bc2b203438c39d05e942cfb0783b3bb9.webp 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_78d037005654202b635b5ad986d36486.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;90&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
